title: Infinite Tai Chi for Health with Jason Chan DVDrip x264 aac MP4
description:
In this DVD Master Jason Chan shows how you can regain physical, emotional and mental well-being in just 20 minutes a day using controlled breathing and simple, flowing body movements.

After leading you through a short series of gentle warm ups, Jason Chan takes you through his Infinite Tai Chi short form. The multi camera work enables you to see movements from a range of angles so that you can follow him with ease and precision.

After you have completed the Short form, you can join Jason in practicing the 5 Elements form of Air, Earth, Fire, Water and Balance which will assist you to combat the stresses and strains of everyday life. Finally Jason will guide you to warm down in a gentle and relaxed way.
